{"id":"int-ee8e3121","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-20T23:15:53.121203Z","actor":"Curt LeCaptain","issue_id":"beads_mobilemusic-pid.3","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"open","reason":"scheduleProviderRecoveryCheck now distinguishes 'provider list still empty' from 'all loaded, all happy'. Before: empty providers array produced empty 'missing' list which took the 'no retry needed' early return. After: if providers.isEmpty at the 15s check, increment a separate emptyProviderListChecks counter (cap 1) and reschedule at +30s. Doesn't burn the providerRecoveryAttempts budget (cap 2) since no reload was triggered. After the reschedule cap, logs 'giving up — no persisted providers?' Build 143; 52 tests pass."}}
